quran[6]{c,v,t,f}:
  6,133,"Olúwa rẹ ni Ọlọ́rọ̀, Aláàánú. Tí Ó bá fẹ́, Ó máa ko yín kúrò (lórí ilẹ̀). Ó sì máa fi ohun tí Ó bá fẹ́ rọ́pò (yín) lẹ́yìn (ìparun) yín gẹ́gẹ́ bí Ó ti ṣe mu yín jáde lẹ́yìn (ìparun) àrọ́mọdọ́mọ àwọn ìjọ mìíràn."
  6,134,"Dájúdájú ohun tí À ń ṣe ní àdéhùn fún yín, ó kúkú ń bọ̀ wá ṣẹlẹ̀; ẹ̀yin kò sì lè dá Allāhu lágara.{1}.",1:[Nípa sísálọ tàbí mímóríbọ́ tàbí ní ọ̀nà mìíràn. Bí àpẹ̀ẹrẹ, sísun ẹ̀dá ní iná dí eérú kò dí àjíǹde rẹ̀ lọ́wọ́ lọ́jọ́ Àjíǹde.]
  6,135,"Sọ pé: “Ẹ̀yin ènìyàn mi, ẹ ṣisẹ́ ní àyè yín. Dájúdájú èmi náà ń ṣiṣẹ́.{1} Láìpẹ́ ẹ̀ máa mọ ẹni tí Ilé Ìkángun-rere (Ọgbà Ìdẹ̀ra) yóò jẹ́ tirẹ̀. Dájúdájú àwọn alábòsí kò níí jèrè.”.",1:[Ìyẹn ni pé, kí olúkùlùkù dúró ti ẹ̀sìn rẹ̀. Irú rẹ̀ tún wà nínú sūrah al-Kāfirūn; 109:6. Ìwọ̀nyẹn wà bẹ́ẹ̀ ṣíwájú àṣẹ ogun ẹ̀sìn.]
  7,43,"A ó sì mú inúnibíni kúrò nínú ọkàn wọn. Àwọn odò yó sì máa ṣàn ní ìsàlẹ̀ wọn. Wọn yóò sọ pé: “Gbogbo ẹyìn ń jẹ́ ti Allāhu, Ẹni tí Ó fi wá mọ̀nà yìí. Àwa ìbá tí mọ̀nà, tí kì í bá ṣe pé Allāhu tọ́ wa sí ọ̀nà. Dájúdájú àwọn Òjíṣẹ́ Olúwa wa ti mú òdodo wá.” Wọ́n sì máa pè wọ́n pé: “Ìyẹn ni Ọgbà Ìdẹ̀ra tí A jogún rẹ̀ fún yín nítorí ohun tí ẹ̀ ń ṣe níṣẹ́.”{1}.",1:[Àànú Allāhu la fi máa wọ inú Ọgbà Ìdẹ̀ra, ṣùgbọ́n a gbọ́dọ̀ ṣe iṣẹ́ Ọgbà Ìdẹ̀ra.]
  7,44,"Àwọn èrò inú Ọgbà Ìdẹ̀ra yóò pe àwọn èrò inú Iná pé: “A ti rí ohun tí Olúwa wa ṣe àdéhùn rẹ̀ fún wa ní òdodo. Ǹjẹ́ ẹ̀yin náà rí ohun tí Olúwa yín ṣe àdéhùn (rẹ̀ fún yín) ní òdodo?” Wọn yóò wí pé: “Bẹ́ẹ̀ ni.” Olùpèpè kan yó sì pèpè láààrin wọn pé: “Kí ibi dandan Allāhu máa bẹ lórí àwọn alábòsí.”"
  7,45,"(Àwọn ni) àwọn tó ń ṣẹ́rí àwọn ènìyàn kúrò lójú ọ̀nà (ẹ̀sìn) Allāhu, wọ́n sì ń fẹ́ kó wọ́. Àwọn sì ni aláìgbàgbọ́ nínú Ọjọ́ Ìkẹ́yìn."